<L>__{exterior a road day}
<A>__{prussian troops on the march. roderick is now one of them. captain galgenstein rides by.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{at the close of the seven years' war, the prussian army, so renowned for its disciplined valor, was officered and under officered by native prussians, it is true, but was composed for the most part of men hired or stolen, like myself, from almost every nation in europe. the deserting to and fro was prodigious.}
